<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">In subsection (b), the words “holding appointments or enlisted in the Regular Air Force as now or hereafter provided by law”, “and such other persons as are now or may hereafter be specified by law”, and “commissioned * * * warrant officers” are omitted as surplusage, since the revised section lists all persons in the Regular Air Force. 10:1832(b) (last sentence) is omitted as executed.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idab61a5bd-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idab61a5be-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2019—<ref href="/us/pl/116/92">Pub. L. 116–92</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s9075">section 9075 of this title</ref> as this section.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2018—<ref href="/us/pl/115/232">Pub. L. 115–232</ref> renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s8075">section 8075 of this title</ref> as <ref href="/us/usc/t10/s9075">section 9075 of this title</ref>.</p>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1958—Subsec. (b)(2). <ref href="/us/pl/85/600">Pub. L. 85–600</ref> included the registrar of the Air Force Academy.</p>
</note>
